#: ../../C/catatonic.rst:5
msgid "catatonic"
msgstr "catatonic"

#: ../../C/catatonic.rst:7
msgid "adj\\."
msgstr "形容詞"

#: ../../C/catatonic.rst:9
msgid ""
"Describes a condition of suspended animation in which something is so "
":ref:`wedged` or :ref:`hung` that it makes no response. If you are typing on"
" a terminal and suddenly the computer doesn't even echo the letters back to "
"the screen as you type, let alone do what you're asking it to do, then the "
"computer is suffering from catatonia (possibly because it has crashed). "
"\"There I was in the middle of a winning game of :ref:`nethack` and it went "
"catatonic on me! Aaargh!\" Compare :ref:`buzz`\\."
msgstr ""
"何かが非常に\\ :ref:`wedged`\\ または\\ :ref:`hung`\\ "
"になって何の反応も示さない、仮死状態を表します。あなたが端末でタイプしているときに、突然コンピューターがあなたの頼んだことを実行するどころか、タイプした文字を画面にエコーバックすることすらしなくなったら、そのコンピューターはカタトニア(緊張病)に苦しんでいます(おそらくクラッシュしたためです)。「\\"
" :ref:`nethack`\\ の勝ちゲームの真っ最中に、こいつがカタトニックになりやがった! ああもう!」 \\ :ref:`buzz`\\ "
"と比較せよ。"
